---
# Repo-wide C / C++ style for school-21.
# Matches the in-tree School 21 .clang-format files
# (materials/linters/.clang-format) — Google style is the
# School 21 convention. Override per-subproject by placing a
# .clang-format file inside the subtree if a project ever needs
# something different.
BasedOnStyle: Google
